Package: cosimmr
Type: Package
Title: A package for running Stable Isotope Mixing Models and including Covariates
Version: 1.0
Date: 2023-08-15
Authors@R:c(person("Emma", "Govan", email = "emma.govan.2021@mumail.ie", role = c("cre","aut")),
          person("Andrew", "Parnell", role = "aut"),
          person("Brice", "Semmens", role = "ctb"),
          person("Eric", "Ward", role = "ctb"),
          person("Brian", "Stock", role = "ctb"),
          person("Andrew", "Jackson", role = "ctb"),
          person("Donald", "Phillips", role = "ctb"))
Maintainer: Emma Govan <emma.govan.2021@mumail.ie>
Description: cosimmr is a package for running Stable Isotope Mixing Models in R. It 
             allows for the inclusion of covariates. The package also has built-in summary functions
             and plot functions which allow for the creation of isospace plots.
License: GPL (>= 2)
